snippet.title: Persona 5 Tactica — Battle Gameplay 1 | Xbox Game Pass, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Windows PC
snippet.description:
Strike hard with all-new gameplay mechanics in Persona 5 Tactica! 🚩

Plan ahead and optimize each member’s skill tree to create the ultimate team synergy or turn the tide of the battle with Triple Threat, the newest take on the classic All-out Attack technique.

Pre-order Persona 5 Tactica now: https://atlus.link/43meT4o
